Description: African Red Slip Ware wheel-made pottery vessel base sherd. Light orange fabric.
Curator's comments: African Red Slip tableware sherd (Hayes 1972). Probably thin walled ware of African Red slip, though the slip is very thin. Hayes, J.W. 1972. Late Roman Pottery. London.
Bibliographic references: Villing et al 2013-2015 / Naukratis: Greeks in Egypt (IF.095) (Phase 3)
